# GitHub Actions

GitHub Actions is GitHub's automation service.

## Purpose
This repository uses GitHub Actions to automatically run the Python program whenever changes are pushed to the repository.

## Workflow
- Trigger: Push to the repository
- Environment: Ubuntu Latest
- Python Version: 3.11
- Command Executed:

```bash
python main.py
```

## Benefits
- Automates testing
- Ensures code runs successfully
- Supports continuous integration (CI)
